lead_paragraph: Switzerland's central bank left interest rates unchanged at record lows, cut its economic outlook and forecast a deeper bout of deflation as cheaper oil and slowing global growth weigh on the economy.

headline.main: Swiss Central Bank Holds Fire on Rates as Inflation Stalls
